Nancy Juvonen  (  born May 18 , 1967  )  is an American film producer .
She and Drew Barrymore own the production company Flower Films .

After Barrymore and Nancy Juvonen formed their joint production company Flower Films in 1995 , it went on to produce several films in which she also starred , such as Never Been Kissed  (  1999  )  , Charlie 's Angels  (  2000  )  , Donnie Darko  (  2001  )  and her directorial debut Whip It !
